(42, 16, 9, 40, 19, 21, 21, NULL, 'Connection of Wealth and Generosity', 'This connection highlights the theme of using wealth for good. Both passages emphasize the importance of giving to the poor and making friends with wealth to secure a future reward.', 'theme', 0.426, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 9, 54, 6, 17, 19, 'everlasting habitations', 'Connection of Wealth and Eternal Life', 'This connection highlights the use of wealth to foster relationships that lead to eternal life. Both passages emphasize the importance of using riches wisely, either by making friends or doing good works, to secure a foundation for the future.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 9, 27, 4, 27, 27, NULL, 'Righteousness and Mercy Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of using resources wisely to benefit others. Luke encourages making friends through unrighteous wealth, while Daniel advises showing mercy to the poor as a means of righteousness.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 9, 40, 6, 24, 24, 'mammon of unrighteousness', 'Connection Between Mammon and Service', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of ''mammon'' as a master that competes with God. Luke 16:9 suggests using ''mammon of unrighteousness'' to gain friends, while Matthew 6:24 warns against serving both God and mammon.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 9, 20, 19, 17, 17, 'friends of the mammon of unrighteousness', 'Connection of Generosity and Reward', 'This connection highlights the theme of using resources to benefit others, as seen in both passages. Luke 16:9 encourages making friends through wealth, while Proverbs 19:17 emphasizes lending to the poor as a service to the Lord, promising a reward.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 9, 42, 14, 14, 14, 'everlasting habitations', 'Blessings and Eternal Recompense', 'This connection highlights the theme of being rewarded in the afterlife for actions taken in this life. Both passages emphasize the idea of being recompensed at the resurrection or in everlasting habitations.', 'theme', 0.37, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 9, 42, 16, 11, 11, NULL, 'Connection of Unrighteous Mammon', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of ''unrighteous mammon'' and the importance of faithfulness in its use. The first verse encourages making friends with it, while the second questions faithfulness in it as a prerequisite for true riches.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
